headline: Prediction: Buying Delta Air Lines Stock Today Will Set You Up for Life
summary: Delta Air Lines will emerge as a stronger airline coming out of the recent slowdown.  Growing loyalty programs, premium travel revenue, and co-brand credit card remuneration are diversifying Delta's revenue streams.  No one should be under any illusions that the air travel market isn't under some pressure right now.
